ic Games in Paris this year.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Yingying_(volleyball)\", \"score\": 0.9999999834619758, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Li Yingying\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Yingying_(volleyball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Yingying_(volleyball)\"}, {\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9402696222070734, \"rank\": 0.054401332743158025, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999128144774, \"rank\": 8.718557856027688e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, she wants to help the team make a difference from the disappointing result at the Tokyo Olympics three years ago.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having arrived in Tokyo as the defending champions, China lost all of their first three matches to T\\u00c3\\u00bcrkiye, USA and the Russian Olympic Committee (ROC) in Pool B.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9982522500168555, \"rank\": 0.0012474371445261466, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9837264583873733, \"rank\": 0.016537598429697833, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", 