ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.7135201911649061, \"rank\": 0.4014999128724475, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We worked hard in training everyday in the past five years.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I underperformed and I am sorry I let coach Lang Ping down.\\\"\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lang_Ping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lang Ping\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lang_Ping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lang_Ping\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Li soon overcame the frustration and grew quickly in the following three years to become an attacking ace of the Chinese national team.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999993471028432, \"rank\": 6.528975770311014e-07, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999995766302, \"