://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999993471028432, \"rank\": 6.528975770311014e-07, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hlai_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After what happened last time, I realized that everyone is fighting to survive at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be fully-prepared for the Olympics this year.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we can stand onto the podium this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": []}]}"